data.description:
Come See This Updated, Move-In Ready Home with Immediate Occupancy! Updates you will love include a New Roof in September 2021, a New Furnace in August 2021, and a new Water Heater in November 2022!
All Appliances to stay with the home, Full Basement, Fenced Yard, a sliding Barn Door on one bedroom, and a Beautiful Large 3 Season Room filled with ample natural sunlight!

Close to highway access!

Terms accepted: FHA, VA, MSHDA, CONVENTIONAL, & CASH
